cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or its data, please cite it as below."
title: "Bouwmelding.nl"
abstract: >
  A client-side web application that displays Dutch government publications
  (bekendmakingen) — including building permits, environmental permits, event
  permits, and other municipal decisions — on an interactive map. Data is
  sourced from the official Dutch government publication repository
  (repository.overheid.nl).
authors:
